## Python [https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Python.gitignore]
## ------

# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[codz]
*$py.class

# C extensions
*.so

# Distribution / packaging
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
